A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a glowing holographic tree structure floating in a dark neon-lit void, where one specific branch and its leaves are brilliantly illuminated in electric cyan while the rest of the tree remains in dim purple wireframe outlines. The illuminated branch appears to be "selected" with data streams and particle effects flowing from it, suggesting the concept of targeting a single component within a larger system. The background features subtle circuit board patterns and floating geometric fragments, creating depth and technological atmosphere. The overall mood is precise, technical, and futuristic with strong contrast between the selected element and its surroundings.
